metadata.name: ♯2 Mike's Falling Asleep
metadata.description:
Mike the Hamster is an NFT creator who distributes his daily life on Youtube.
In his Vlogs, the only footage that plays is of him sleeping.
This is a collection of his sleeping scenes.

Mike fell asleep while working on an NFT exhibit on his laptop. Mike was a night owl because he fell asleep yesterday evening.

PCでNFT出品作業中に寝てしまったマイク。昨日夕方に寝てしまったせいで、夜更かしになってしまった。
